'''Magnus Lindkvist''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[Cavendish Invitational|Cavendish Invitational Pairs]] (1) 1988


===Runners-up===

* [[Rosenblum Cup]] (1) 2006 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-open-teams.aspx Rosenblum Cup Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (2)
